            <title>[WFLY-5498] Transaction probe needlessly locks CLI</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-5498</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A transaction probe grabs the controller lock before proceeding.  Transaction probes may see long run times depending upon db responsiveness.  So other CLI operations can end up needlessly blocked for quite some time waiting for the db to respond for a transaction probe to proceed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
